'''庫雷薩雷城堡'''（{{lang-et|Kuressaare linnus}}；{{lang-de|Schloss Arensburg}}）或稱'''庫雷薩雷主教城堡'''（{{lang-et|Kuressaare piiskopilinnus}}）是位於[[愛沙尼亞|愛沙尼亞]]西部[[薩雷馬島|薩雷馬島]]城市[[庫雷薩雷|庫雷薩雷]]上的一座[[城堡|城堡]]。城堡的歷史可以追溯至1380年代<ref name="Viirand 2004 176–178">{{cite book | last = Viirand| first = Tiiu| authorlink = | title = Estonia. Cultural Tourism | publisher = Kunst Publishers | series = | volume = | edition = | year = 2004 | location = | pages = 176–178 | language = | url = | doi = | id = | isbn = 9949-407-18-4 | mr = | zbl = | jfm = }}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
最早提到庫雷薩雷城堡的文獻紀載是在1380年代，當時[[條頓騎士團|條頓騎士團]]開始為{{tsl|en|Bishopric of Ösel–Wiek|薩雷馬－萊內主教區}}的{{tsl|et|Saare-Lääne piiskop|薩雷馬－萊內主教|主教}}們興建城堡<ref name="Viirand 2004 176–178"/>，且有資料指出首座城堡是由木頭所建造<ref name="O'Connor2006">{{cite book|last=O'Connor|first=Kevin|title=Culture And Customs of the Baltic States|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8Dl2i1Fkd_cC&pg=PA207|accessdate=2012-06-04|year=2006|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|isbn=978-0-313-33125-1|page=207}}</ref><ref name="JarvisOchser2011">{{cite book|last1=Jarvis|first1=Howard|last2=Ochser|first2=Tim|title=DK Eyewitness Travel Guide: Estonia, Latvia & Lithuania|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=r3HAJH39SP4C&pg=PA32|accessdate=2012-06-04|date=2011-05-02|publisher=Dorling Kindersley|isbn=978-1-4053-6063-0|page=32}}</ref>。當時[[薩雷馬島|薩雷馬島]]居民激烈抵抗[[立窩尼亞十字軍入侵|立窩尼亞十字軍的入侵]]，庫雷薩雷城堡無疑是十字軍為控制該島所建造的堡壘。直到城堡在16世紀的[[立窩尼亞戰爭|立窩尼亞戰爭]]遭拆解以前，庫雷薩雷城堡一直是薩雷馬－萊內主教治下的要塞，並且長期是該區最重要的城堡之一。<ref name="History of the castle and fortress">{{cite web|url = http://www.saaremaamuuseum.ee/en/castle-and-fortress/history-of-the-castle-and-fortress/|title = History of the castle and fortress|last = |first = |date = |publisher = Saaremaa Muuseum|accessdate = 2012-12-26|language = en|archive-date = 2020-08-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200829073158/http://www.saaremaamuuseum.ee/en/castle-and-fortress/history-of-the-castle-and-fortress/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

[[File:Saaremaa_Museum_SM_F_3761_245_F,_Kuressaare_linnus,_kindluse_plaan_1710._aastast.jpg|thumb]]
1559年，[[丹麥|丹麥]]取得薩雷馬島和庫雷薩雷城堡的控制權，並且對城堡的防禦工程進行現代化改造，《{{tsl|en|Second Treaty of Brömsebro (1645)|布勒姆瑟布魯條約}}》簽訂後，[[瑞典帝國|瑞典]]和[[丹麥-挪威|丹麥]]結束{{tsl|en|Torstenson War|托爾斯騰森戰爭}}，薩雷馬島轉為瑞典統治，該國持續對庫雷薩雷城堡進行現代化改造。直至1706年[[大北方戰爭|大北方戰爭]]後，薩雷馬島和庫雷薩雷城堡成為[[俄羅斯帝國|俄羅斯帝國]]的一部分。<ref name="History of the castle and fortress"/>

隨著俄羅斯帝國的疆域向西推進，庫雷薩雷城堡逐漸失去其戰略價值，尤其在[[芬蘭戰爭|芬蘭戰爭]]和[[第三次瓜分波蘭|第三次瓜分波蘭]]後，軍事重心自愛沙尼亞轉移。1836年，[[奧蘭|奧蘭]]群島上的{{tsl|fi|Bomarsund|博瑪爾松德城堡}}建成，俄羅斯將庫雷薩雷城堡的駐軍撤離<ref name="History of the castle and fortress"/>，之後該城堡也未在[[克里米亞戰爭|克里米亞戰爭]]中被使用，亦說明其失去了戰略意義。<ref>{{cite book | last = Taylor| first = Neil| authorlink = | title = Estonia | publisher = Bradt Travel Guides Ltd. | series = | volume = | edition = 6| year = 2010| location = | page = [https://archive.org/details/estoniabradttrav0000tayl/page/254 254] | language = | url =https://archive.org/details/estoniabradttrav0000tayl| doi = | id = | isbn = 978-1-84162-320-7 | mr = | zbl = | jfm = }}</ref>19世纪時，庫雷薩雷城堡成為[[貧民窟|貧民窟]]。<ref name="History of the castle and fortress"/>1904－1912年，[[波羅的海德意志人|波羅的海德意志]]建築師{{tsl|en|Wilhelm Neumann|威廉·諾伊曼}}和{{tsl|et|Karl Rudolf Hermann Seuberlich|赫曼·塞伯里奇}}對庫雷薩雷城堡進行修復。<ref name="History of the castle and fortress"/>

1941年，庫雷薩雷城堡被[[蘇聯|蘇聯]][[蘇聯佔領波羅的海國家|佔領]]並作為軍事據點，[[蘇聯紅軍|蘇聯紅軍]]在城堡外院處決了90位平民，隨後在{{tsl|en|German occupation of Estonia during World War II|第二次世界戰德國對愛沙尼亞的占領|納粹德國的入侵}}中，有超過300人在城堡內被殺害。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Dragicevich |first1=Peter |last2=Ragozin |first2=Leonid |title=Lonely Planet Estonia, Latvia & Lithuania |date=2016 |publisher=Lonely Planet Global Limited |isbn=9781760341442 |url=https://www.google.com/books/edition/Lonely_Planet_Estonia_Latvia_Lithuania/ce78CwAAQBAJ?hl=en&gbpv=1&dq=kuressaare+castle+execution&pg=PT353&printsec=frontcover |accessdate=2020-06-26 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829073156/https://www.google.com/books/edition/Lonely_Planet_Estonia_Latvia_Lithuania/ce78CwAAQBAJ?hl=en&gbpv=1&dq=kuressaare+castle+execution&pg=PT353&printsec=frontcover |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=1941 EXECUTIONS IN KURESSAARE CASTLE |url=https://singingrevolution.com/img/TSR/pages/section_01/1941_Executions_in_Kuressaare_Castle.pdf |website=Singing Revolution |publisher=Saarte Hääl Newspaper (“Voice of the Islands”) |date=1988-09-13 |accessdate=2020-06-26 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829073156/https://singingrevolution.com/img/TSR/pages/section_01/1941_Executions_in_Kuressaare_Castle.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Saaremaa Museum, Kuressaare |url=http://coldwarsites.net/country/estonia/saaremaa-museum-kuressaare/ |publisher=The Baltic Initiative And Network |accessdate=2020-06-26 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829073159/http://coldwarsites.net/country/estonia/saaremaa-museum-kuressaare/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Kuressaare Castle |url=http://www.spottinghistory.com:80/view/446/kuressaare-castle/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610144302/http://www.spottinghistory.com/view/446/kuressaare-castle/ |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2016-06-10 |publisher=Spotting History |accessdate=2020-06-26 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Kuressaare Episcopal Castle |url=https://www.lonelyplanet.com/estonia/southwestern-estonia-and-the-islands/kuressaare/attractions/kuressaare-episcopal-castle/a/poi-sig/455369/359134 |accessdate=2020-08-28 |publisher=Lonely Planet |language=en |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829073202/https://www.lonelyplanet.com/estonia/southwestern-estonia-and-the-islands/kuressaare/attractions/kuressaare-episcopal-castle/a/poi-sig/455369/359134 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1968年，愛沙尼亞建築師{{tsl|et|Kalvi Aluve|卡爾維·阿盧韋}}對庫雷薩雷城堡進行二次修復。<ref name="LangLaneman2006">{{cite book|last1=Lang|first1=V.|last2=Laneman|first2=Margot|title=Archaeological research in Estonia, 1865-2005|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xJciAQAAIAAJ|accessdate=2012-06-04|year=2006|publisher=Tartu University Press|page=185}}</ref>該城堡現已成為薩雷馬博物館（Saaremaa Muuseum）的所在地。<ref name="History of the castle and fortress"/>

== 建築 ==
[[File:Kuressaare_piiskopilinnus_-_Põhjabastioni_suurtükitorn.JPG|thumb]]
庫雷薩雷城堡被認為是愛沙尼亞保持最完好的中世紀防禦建築之一。<ref name="Viirand 2004 176–178"/>

城堡的建築風格屬於[[哥德式建築|哥德式晚期]]，特色是形式簡單，城堡內的修道院式結構是圍繞著中央庭園的方型建築，而在北角的防禦塔高{{convert|37|m|ft}}。1980年代修復了一座沿著城垛的防禦長廊，而城堡的{{tsl|en|Portcullis|垂降柵欄}}和大門均有重建。城堡內部則作為儲藏用的地窖，並配有{{tsl|en|Central heating|中央暖氣|中央暖氣系統}}，主樓內有城堡最重要的房間，另外有一座將所有主要房間連結的迴廊，包括[[食堂|食堂]]、宿舍、小教堂和主教的臥室，城堡後方展示11座薩雷馬貴族使用巴洛克式雕刻的[[墓誌銘|墓誌銘]]。<ref name="History of the castle and fortress"/><ref>{{cite journal |last1= Tvauri|first1= Andres|date= Autumn 2009|title= Late medieval hypocausts with heat storage in Estonia|journal= Baltic Journal of Art History |volume= |issue= |page= 52|publisher= Institute of History and Archaeology of the University of Tartu|doi= }}</ref>

14世紀末到15世紀初，城堡周圍修建了一條長{{convert|625|m|ft}}的城牆，由於武器技術進步，城堡在16－17世紀間又增加了防禦措施。由瑞典軍事工程師{{tsl|en|Erik Dahlbergh |埃里克·達赫伯格}}設計的[[塞巴斯蒂安·勒普雷斯特·德·沃邦|沃邦式]]堡壘和{{tsl|en|Ravelin|半月堡}}基本保持完好。1711年[[大北方戰爭|大北方戰爭]]期間，俄羅斯帝國駐軍離開時故意炸毀城堡大部分的防禦裝置，後來其中一部分又被重新修復。<ref name="History of the castle and fortress"/>1861年，在[[里加|里加]]建築師H.格金根（H.Göggingen）的監督下，開始將庫雷薩雷城堡改建為公園。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Kuressaare Castle Park |url=http://www.kuressaare.ee/uus/kuressaare-castle-park/ |accessdate=2020-08-29 |date=2011-06-03 |publisher=Kuressaare Municipality |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304030925/http://www.kuressaare.ee/uus/kuressaare-castle-park/ |archivedate=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>

